reviewText: Gene Autry collection vol. 10 has 4 more of his early movies at there best in his frist western 1935 and they are all uncut and fully restored like they were just released.
Love these Gene Autry movies they are a must to buy
I'm a big fan of Gene's, and collecting all his work.
All of these collections are very good transfers.
I love campy westerns and Gene Autry's westerns bring back great times as a child. These remastered westerns are fairly good quality most everyone who enjoys the genre will appreciate.
Here we have 4 Gene Autry fast paced and full of music movies.  If you are a Gene Autry fan you will enjoy this DVD pack.  I recommend this one to be added to your collection.
Good price, hard to find elsewhere

The previous Autry releases have been restored uncut prints. However, in Volume 10 "Oh Susanna" is the standard MCA cut print running 53 minutes. The DVD states the running time as 59 minutes, but it is in fact edited. The other titles are all restored and complete. Hopefully, this will not become the norm with Timeless Media, who already have a bad reputation. Fingers crossed....
Great product and service. Thanks again.
